Class ClassFieldMapper<C>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.zethmayr.benjamin.spring.common.mapper.base.ClassFieldMapper<C>

    public abstract class ClassFieldMapper<C>
extends Object
    A mapper for any specific field of a given class.
